<p>Due payment failure, we have cancelled your recurring contribution of
{{currency order.totalAmount currency=order.currency}} to {{collective.name}}.

We are sad to see you go. You can restart your contribution anytime at <a href="https://opencollective.com/{{collective.slug}}">https://opencollective.com/{{collective.slug}}</a>.</p>

{{else}}

<p>We are having trouble processing your payment of {{currency order.totalAmount currency=order.currency}} to {{collective.name}}.</p>

